561de97b-a518-42df-b7fb-e7e7c21ac252.title: Father Aereck
561de97b-a518-42df-b7fb-e7e7c21ac252.text: Welcome to the church of holy Saradomin.

c1cbd27a-8a37-4fb6-a14b-0fe5cc77c2b4.title: Father Aereck
c1cbd27a-8a37-4fb6-a14b-0fe5cc77c2b4.text: It is, isn't it? It was built over 230 years ago.

8756e033-b818-4df3-98a4-0c2e9f2fc2c4.title: Father Aereck
8756e033-b818-4df3-98a4-0c2e9f2fc2c4.text: Surely you have heard of the god, Saradomin?

e15a30a5-9d74-4dd4-b3e8-7daeb6c14876.title: Father Aereck
e15a30a5-9d74-4dd4-b3e8-7daeb6c14876.text:
He who creates the forces of goodness and purity in
this world? I cannot believe your ignorance!

e1941cf1-ff2e-4117-887d-7ba0bb9d4c85.title: Father Aereck
e1941cf1-ff2e-4117-887d-7ba0bb9d4c85.text:
This is the god with more followers than any other! ...At
least in this part of the world.

4f3a2aa3-b805-4eaa-82a9-0b5c92595e7d.title: Father Aereck
4f3a2aa3-b805-4eaa-82a9-0b5c92595e7d.text:
He who created this world along with his brothers
Guthix and Zamorak?

options.text: Oh, sorry. I'm not from this world.

676151dc-9ce2-4e0c-8011-6f9a93620523.title: <player>
676151dc-9ce2-4e0c-8011-6f9a93620523.text: Oh, sorry. I'm not from this world.

9b15a7f3-61d9-4722-8b49-55cc0e64907c.title: Father Aereck
9b15a7f3-61d9-4722-8b49-55cc0e64907c.text:
I thought things not from this world were all... You
know. Slime and tentacles.

options.text: You don't understand. This is an online game!
I am - do you like my disguise?

582ea10f-c3fb-4994-9088-4011982b3abe.title: <player>
582ea10f-c3fb-4994-9088-4011982b3abe.text: I am - do you like my disguise?

517100c4-c01a-428d-a0af-b2298764e8e8.title: Father Aereck
517100c4-c01a-428d-a0af-b2298764e8e8.text:
Aargh! Avaunt foul creature from another dimension!
Avaunt! Begone in the name of Saradomin!

fc97da64-c3ed-4cb6-9745-3ffc852f5af7.title: <player>
fc97da64-c3ed-4cb6-9745-3ffc852f5af7.text: Ok, ok, I was only joking...

c5e3e992-220b-445f-9cb6-8af6446583b7.title: <player>
c5e3e992-220b-445f-9cb6-8af6446583b7.text: Yeah... I, uh, thought you said something else.

24924e5d-bd09-4c6d-83c7-665babc171d2.title: <player>
24924e5d-bd09-4c6d-83c7-665babc171d2.text: You don't understand. This is an online game!

10cfc580-2298-456e-8d8b-e9eea6b7d49d.title: Father Aereck
10cfc580-2298-456e-8d8b-e9eea6b7d49d.text: That's lucky, I need someone to do a quest for me.

options.text: Sorry, I don't have time right now

ea7fb798-b65c-472e-b13b-df09064b0c1a.title: <player>
ea7fb798-b65c-472e-b13b-df09064b0c1a.text: Sorry, I don't have time right now

d0cfa3c7-061c-4113-82c3-7020818a9b92.title: Father Aereck
d0cfa3c7-061c-4113-82c3-7020818a9b92.text:
Oh well. If you do have some spare time on your
hands, come back and talk to me.

2924bfb7-93a7-4254-bdfe-84d32fac557d.title: Father Aereck
2924bfb7-93a7-4254-bdfe-84d32fac557d.text:
Thank you. The problem is, there is a ghost in the
church graveyard. I would like you to get rid of it.

91f40d3b-7d57-441e-afd8-0749e6b8c17b.title: Father Aereck
91f40d3b-7d57-441e-afd8-0749e6b8c17b.text:
If you need any help, my friend Father Urhney is an
expert on ghosts.

aa347e22-7fe4-4a27-b1ba-284224ecced3.title: Father Aereck
aa347e22-7fe4-4a27-b1ba-284224ecced3.text:
I believe he is currently living as a hermit in Lumbridge
swamp. He has a little shack in the south-west of the
swamps.

9ce15103-a51a-4e5c-8c8d-216bb1240756.title: Father Aereck
9ce15103-a51a-4e5c-8c8d-216bb1240756.text:
Exit the graveyard through the south gate to reach the
swamp. I'm sure if you told him that I sent you he'd
be willing to help.

ad870dcd-45fd-43c1-afde-168c50f9b96d.title: Father Aereck
ad870dcd-45fd-43c1-afde-168c50f9b96d.text:
My name is Father Aereck by the way. Pleased to
meet you.

446db21d-8fd4-4f0a-a781-1daa6273473d.title: Father Aereck
446db21d-8fd4-4f0a-a781-1daa6273473d.text:
Take care travelling through the swamps, I have heard
they can be quite dangerous.

f95c648c-d412-429b-a49b-b381582901e5.title: Father Aereck
f95c648c-d412-429b-a49b-b381582901e5.text: Have you got rid of the ghost yet?

5322ea92-b280-4a27-b407-8e5431e6637f.title: <player>
5322ea92-b280-4a27-b407-8e5431e6637f.text: I can't find Father Urhney at the moment.ghost yet?

a0c7dced-82e7-4670-8284-2ebf8e9040b3.title: Father Aereck
a0c7dced-82e7-4670-8284-2ebf8e9040b3.text:
Well, you can get to the swamp he lives in by going
south through the cemetery.

c27ef6cc-7606-4d52-ac6b-4fd9eb60d82d.title: Father Aereck
c27ef6cc-7606-4d52-ac6b-4fd9eb60d82d.text:
You'll have to go right into the western depths of the
swamp, near the coastline. That is where his house is.

5c30a5ed-8dda-4b87-8c7b-6d1703f55fa8.title: Father Aereck
5c30a5ed-8dda-4b87-8c7b-6d1703f55fa8.text: Have you got rid of the ghost yet?

31b677aa-5e22-4a34-acae-831c676f8505.title: <player>
31b677aa-5e22-4a34-acae-831c676f8505.text:
I had a talk with Father Urhney. He has given me this
funny amulet to talk to the ghost with.

f797624d-39f9-4589-9823-8a6cadadb5ea.title: Father Aereck
f797624d-39f9-4589-9823-8a6cadadb5ea.text:
I always wondered what that amulet was... Well, I hope
it's useful. Tell me when you get rid of the ghost!

3384cc90-db26-4fb3-bc19-76a5b58c4b8b.title: Father Aereck
3384cc90-db26-4fb3-bc19-76a5b58c4b8b.text: Have you got rid of the ghost yet?

a679f3bd-6ef0-4115-adda-ded15ecfddf3.title: <player>
a679f3bd-6ef0-4115-adda-ded15ecfddf3.text:
I've found out that the ghost's corpse has lost its skull.
If I can find the skull, the ghost should leave.

05af116c-8499-47a7-a445-d7d124e165e9.title: Father Aereck
05af116c-8499-47a7-a445-d7d124e165e9.text: Hmmmmm. Well, I haven't seen any skulls.

03c63716-883a-4bf9-8798-6811afd9df48.title: <player>
03c63716-883a-4bf9-8798-6811afd9df48.text: Yes, I think a warlock has stolen it.

b1564bae-61c4-4b79-b1a0-edced38cdbc7.title: Father Aereck
b1564bae-61c4-4b79-b1a0-edced38cdbc7.text: Have you got rid of the ghost yet?

5493c6a5-5728-4e15-b788-597ddad3d7f6.title: <player>
5493c6a5-5728-4e15-b788-597ddad3d7f6.text: I've finally found the ghost's skull!

96e489a0-8e51-4fa5-8874-b059396b7f7c.title: Father Aereck
96e489a0-8e51-4fa5-8874-b059396b7f7c.text:
Great! Put it in the ghost's coffin and see what
happens!

118b488c-1ee5-4417-ab88-03388c91e5d4.title: Father Aereck
118b488c-1ee5-4417-ab88-03388c91e5d4.text:
Thank you for getting rid of that awful ghost for me!
May Saradomin always smile upon you!

b4d0a9ff-7e52-4e47-9d43-e36ec3914aa9.title: <player>
b4d0a9ff-7e52-4e47-9d43-e36ec3914aa9.text: I'm looking for a new quest.

1a948927-7698-4e3e-bd32-fb35aba189f8.title: Father Aereck
1a948927-7698-4e3e-bd32-fb35aba189f8.text: Sorry, I only had the one quest.
